@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Welcome to CathSpeak";
    Layout = "_LayoutPublic";
}

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="main-nav">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="/img/image35.png" alt="CathSpeak Logo" />
            </div>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/Courses">Courses</a>
                <a href="/About">About us</a>
                <a href="/Pricing">Pricing</a>
                <a href="/Blog">Blog</a>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-actions">
                <div class="language-selector">
                    <span>English</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </div>
                <a href="/Auth/Register" class="btn btn-light btn-sm">Get started</a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <h1>
                    <span class="text-accent">A</span> unique <span class="text-gold">approach to</span><br />
                    learning foreign<br />
                    languages online
                </h1>
                <p>Learn at your own pace, with lifetime<br />access on mobile and desktop</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="/Auth/Register" class="btn btn-accent">Get started</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img src="/img/image.png" alt="Student with notebooks" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Values Section -->
<section class="values-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="section-label">WHY CHOOSE US</span>
            <h2>Our values</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon blue">
                    <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Speaking clubs</h3>
                <p>In our school you will practice your speaking skills and just get a lot of positive emotions!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon orange">
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Quality control</h3>
                <p>A huge work has been done with the teachers and their work has been monitored thoroughly.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-card">
                <div class="value-icon purple">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                </div>
                <h3>Progress analysis</h3>
                <p>The CEF of Reference has been used at our school. It allows to control our students' success in studying.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="section-label">MORE INFO</span>
            <h2>Common questions</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-column">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How can I know my level of knowledge?</h3>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We offer a free assessment test to determine your current language proficiency level. Based on the results, we'll recommend the most suitable course for you.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Can I do it individually or only in a group?</h3>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We offer both individual and group learning options. You can choose the format that works best for your learning style and schedule.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>What is the maximum group size?</h3>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Our group classes are kept small with a maximum of 8 students to ensure quality instruction and ample speaking time for each participant.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-column">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Do I need to buy materials for lessons?</h3>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>All learning materials are included with your course and are available digitally. No additional purchases are necessary.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Are you adjusting to the student's schedule?</h3>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, we offer flexible scheduling options to accommodate your availability and time zone.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item active">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How the first lesson with teacher will be?</h3>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-minus-circle"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer visible">
                        <p>By the end of the trial lesson, you will be able to determine for yourself whether this kind of online lesson is right for you or not. In our experience, most students appreciate the benefits of online education and decide to study online.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

